# TrailVerse Backend API

Entry: `server/server.js` → `server/src/app.js`. Base path: **`/api`**. Swagger: `/api-docs`. Health: `/health` (not under `/api`).

## Auth middleware (`server/src/middleware/auth.js`)

| Middleware | Use |
|------------|-----|
| `protect` | Requires `Authorization: Bearer <JWT>` → `req.user` |
| `admin` | After protect; `req.user.role === 'admin'` |
| `optionalAuth` | Sets user or null; never 401 |

JWT: `JWT_SECRET`, `JWT_EXPIRE` (default 7d). Token generation: `utils/generateToken.js`.

## Route mount order (critical)

- `enhancedParks` mounted **before** `parks` on `/api/parks`
- Blog `GET /:slug` registered **last** in `blogs.js`
- Comments mounted at `/api` root: `/blogs/:blogId/comments`

## Domain quick reference

### `/api/auth`
`signup`, `login`, `logout`, `me`, `forgot-password`, `reset-password/:token`, `verify-email/:token`, `migrate-chat` (protect)

### `/api/parks` + enhanced
- List, `/:parkCode` and sub-resources: alerts, activities, campgrounds, places, tours, webcams, videos, gallery, parkinglots, transit, brochures, permits, facilities
- **Search** (intent landings + MCP): `GET /search?q=` — token match + trait scoring; optional `pinned=` (comma-separated park codes). Match copy: `server/src/catalog/matchExplanation.js`, traits: `traitBuilder.js`, query intent: `queryTraitIntent.js`, pins: `server/data/search-intent-pins.json`
- Enhanced: `/:parkCode/enhanced`, `weather`, `crowd`, `best-time`, `reviews`
- Compare: `GET|POST /compare`, `/compare/summary`

### `/api/discover`
`catalog`, `detail`, `parks`, `nps-guide` — all public

### `/api/trips` (Plan AI persistence)
- `GET /shared/:shareId` — **public**
- All other routes: `protect`
- CRUD + `/:tripId/messages`, `/:tripId/share`

### `/api/ai`
- `chat`, `chat-stream` — protect
- `chat-anonymous`, `session-status/:anonymousId`, `providers-anonymous` — public
- `realtime-session` — optionalAuth
- `voice-tool` — public callback
- Feedback sub-router under `/api/ai/feedback` — protect

### `/api/blogs`
Public: list, categories, tags, `/:slug`, view count  
Admin: CRUD, publish-scheduled  
Engagement: like/favorite — optionalAuth

### `/api/users`, `/api/user`, `/api/users/preferences`
Profile, saved-parks, visited-parks, password change, GDPR export/delete — all `protect` unless noted in master route list

### `/api/reviews`, `/api/testimonials`, `/api/events`, `/api/feed`
See `01-frontend-pages.mdc` for product mapping

### `/api/admin`, `/api/analytics`
All `protect` + `admin`

### `/api/gmaps`
Server-side Google Maps proxy — **never expose** `GMAPS_SERVER_KEY` to client

### `/api/images`
`GET /file/*` public; upload/management protect

