| Model | Role |
|-------|------|
| User | Auth, role, profile |
| TripPlan | Plan AI trips, messages, shareId |
| AnonymousSession | Pre-login chat |
| BlogPost, Comment | CMS |
| ParkReview | User reviews |
| Favorite, VisitedPark, UserPreferences | User park data |
